summary: This is an email chain from March 25, 2021, discussing the completion of data copying and submission to an Ops Team, with a reference to 'Maxwell/Epstein scanning by the Florida place that was done wrong by them multiple times.' The document appears to relate to data handling in the context of the Epstein/Maxwell case.

events.title: Data copying and submission completed
events.description: The copying of data was completed and submitted to the Ops Team for loading, with instructions provided to a specialist and marked as a top priority.

keyFacts: Data copying related to 'Maxwell/Epstein scanning' was completed on March 25, 2021.
The data was submitted to an Ops Team for loading, marked as a top priority.
There is a reference to scanning done by 'the Florida place' that was 'done wrong by them multiple times' in relation to Maxwell/Epstein.
